Doubleline’s Gundlach Takes Witness Stand in Trial With TCW

-- B y   E d v a r d   P e t t e r s s o n
-- 
2011-08-11T20:05:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/doubleline-s-gundlach-takes-witness-stand-in-trial-over-2009-firing-by-tcw.html
DoubleLine Capital LP’s  Jeffrey
Gundlach  took the witness stand in a jury trial that pits him
against his former employer, TCW Group Inc., over who betrayed
whom when the firm fired him in 2009.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edvard Pettersson in Los Angeles at 
